    {
      "type": "text",
      "body": "This blog is on my four day trip to Phuket and Phi Phi Islands, Thailand.  The trip began with my group flying from Singapore to Phuket on Thursday afternoon."
    },
    {
      "type": "row",
      "body": [
        {
          "type": "image",
          "body": "phuket/IMG_0963.JPG",
          "caption": "Our pickup spot"
        },
        {
          "type": "image",
          "body": "phuket/IMG_0965.JPG",
          "caption": "Mini bus"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "body": "After we landed, we got in a taxi that turned out to be a party bus and drove an hour to our hostel.  The hostel was very nice, and we put our things away before checking out some of the nearby streets."
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "body": "phuket/IMG_0967.JPG",
      "caption": "Street view"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "body": "The next day, we rode to Kamala beach, which was a 45 minute drive north. "
    },
    {
      "type": "row",
      "body": [
        {
          "type": "image",
          "body": "phuket/IMG_0004.JPG",
          "caption": "On the way"
        },
        {
          "type": "image",
          "body": "phuket/IMG_0971.JPG",
          "caption": "From the car"
        },
        {
          "type": "image",
          "body": "phuket/IMG_0003.JPG",
          "caption": "The beach"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "body": "We hung out at that beach for most of the day, and then watched the sunset on the beach closer to our hostel."
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "body": "The next day, we took a ferry to Koh Phi Phi Don, where we would stay for the next two nights."
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "body": "phuket/IMG_0982.JPG",
      "caption": "Approaching our destination"
    },
    {
      "type": "row",
      "caption": "Islands along the way",
      "body": [
        {
          "type": "image",
          "body": "phuket/IMG_0986.JPG"
        },
        {
          "type": "image",
