          "body": "phuket/IMG_0989.JPG"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "body": "Once there, we had dinner and hiked to a sightseeing spot near the top of one side of the island."
    },
    {
      "type": "row",
      "caption": "Views from the top",
      "body": [
        {
          "type": "image",
          "body": "phuket/IMG_0990.JPG"
        },
        {
          "type": "image",
          "body": "phuket/IMG_0992.JPG"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "body": "The next day, we woke up early and did a boat tour of some surrounding areas."
    },
    {
      "type": "row",
      "body": [
        {
          "type": "image",
          "body": "phuket/IMG_0999.JPG",
          "caption": "On the way"
        },
        {
          "type": "image",
          "body": "phuket/IMG_1003.JPG",
          "caption": "Viking cove"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "body": "We first swam in a lagoon; the water was great."
    },
    {
      "type": "row",
      "caption": "Lagoon",
      "body": [
        {
          "type": "image",
          "body": "phuket/IMG_1005.JPG"
        },
        {
          "type": "image",
          "body": "phuket/IMG_0002.JPG"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "body": "We then went to Maya bay, which is apparently the location of ‘The Beach (2000)’.  I have never seen the movie, but as it turns out Phi Phi Islands gained most of their popularity after its release."
    },
    {
      "type": "row",
      "caption": "Maya Bay",
      "body": [
        {
          "type": "image",
          "body": "phuket/IMG_1008.JPG"
        },
        {
          "type": "image",
          "body": "phuket/IMG_0001.JPG"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "body": "We then headed back and had a relaxing afternoon.  A few hours later, Hugo and I decided to go kayaking in the bay near our hostel.  We made it almost to sea, and got to see a cool rock formation near the ocean."
    },
    {
